doctype html

html
	head
		title Dissenter Blue Extension - Options
		meta(charset="utf-8")
		link(href='./options.css' type='text/css' rel='stylesheet')

	
	body
		div(class='main')
			

			header(class='header fixed')
				div(class='header__inner')
					img(class='header__img-logo' src='../assets/images/logo/gab-logo.png')
					h1(class='header__title') Dissenter Extension &mdash; Options
					span(class='header__subtitle') Close this page when you're done
			

			div(class='content rel')
				div(class='content__inner')
					

					//- BLOCK - Context Menu
					div(class='input-block')
						div(class='input-block__meta no-select')
							span(class='input-block__meta-title') Content Scripts
							span(class='input-block__meta-subtitle')
								| "Content scripts" are scripts that run in specific web pages.
								| By using the standard Document Object Model (DOM), these scripts are able to make changes to those websites in order to enhance the experience.
						div(class='input-block__items')

							label(class='input-block-item no-select')
								input(id='twitter-enabled' class='input-block-item__checkbox' type='checkbox' checked='')
								| Twitter Enabled
							label(class='input-block-item no-select')
								input(id='reddit-enabled' class='input-block-item__checkbox' type='checkbox' checked='')
								| Reddit Enabled
							label(class='input-block-item no-select')
								input(id='youtube-enabled' class='input-block-item__checkbox' type='checkbox' checked='')
								| YouTube Enabled
							label(class='input-block-item no-select')
								input(id='window-sidebar-enabled' class='input-block-item__checkbox' type='checkbox' checked='')
								| Open new window when sidebar unavailable (Firefox only)
							label(class='input-block-item no-select')
								input(id='comment-badge-enabled' class='input-block-item__checkbox' type='checkbox' checked='')
								| Comment Badge Enabled
							label(class='input-block-item no-select')
								input(id='disqus-dissent-enabled' class='input-block-item__checkbox' type='checkbox' checked='')
								| Disqus Dissent Button Enabled
								
					//- BLOCK - Permissions
					div(class='input-block')
						div(class='input-block__meta no-select')
							span(class='input-block__meta-title') About Browser Permissions
						div(class='input-block__items input-block__items--full')
							p(class='input-block-item__paragraph')
								b Active Tab:&nbsp;
								| The "Active Tab" permission gives this extension temporary access to the currently active tab when the you invoke the extension.&nbsp;
								| Access to the tab lasts while the you are on that page, and is revoked when the you navigates away or closes the tab.

					//- BLOCK - Contact
					div(class='input-block')
						div(class='input-block__meta no-select')
							span(class='input-block__meta-title') Contact
						div(class='input-block__items input-block__items--full')

							p(class='input-block-item__paragraph')
								| Dissenter Blue is based on 
								a(class='input-block-item__paragraph-link' rel='noreferrer nofollow' href='https://github.com/gab-ai-inc/gab-dissenter-extension' target='_blank') Dissenter by Gab
								br
								| Try to avoid contacting Gab about any bugs, questions, ideas for Dissenter Blue.
								br
								br
								| If you have something to report, please leave an issue at:
								br
								a(class='input-block-item__paragraph-link' rel='noreferrer nofollow' href='https://github.com/Kippykip/gab-dissenter-extension' target='_blank') github.com/Kippykip/gab-dissenter-extension
							p(class='input-block-item__paragraph') Please be mindful that when submitting a post, more is better. Include any and all information related to your query, use photos or videos if possible.
							p(class='input-block-item__paragraph input-block-item__paragraph--about-extension') 
								b Browser:&nbsp;
								span(id='extension-about__browser') __BROWSER_NAME__
								br
								b Version:&nbsp;
								span(id='extension-about__version') __VERSION__-Blue
								br
								b Download:&nbsp;
								a(class='input-block-item__paragraph-link' rel='noreferrer nofollow' href='https://github.com/Kippykip/gab-dissenter-extension/releases' target='_blank') github.com/Kippykip/gab-dissenter-extension/releases
							p(class='input-block-item__paragraph center input-block-item__paragraph--about-extension') 
								| Dissenter is Copyright &copy; 2019 Gab AI, Inc.

		script(src='./options.js')
